# Fruit Frenzy Survival

## Description

Fruit Frenzy Survival is a Scratch game created for Harvard University's CS50 course.

The player controls a ball using the WASD keys and must survive until the countdown timer reaches zero while avoiding the Apple and Banana enemies.

## Controls

- W = Move Up
- A = Move Left
- S = Move Down
- D = Move Right

## Features

- WASD movement
- Countdown timer
- Random enemy movement
- Enemy chase behavior
- Game Over screen
- Victory screen

## Objective

Survive until the timer reaches zero without touching the Apple or Banana.

